Do you know anything about Bourbon? Its one of those drinks we rarely talk about maybe in movies.  In fact, we probably drink it, but we don’t know that we are having Bourbon. Personally, I have had so many Bourbon based cocktails, but haven’t ever researched on the history, and what it’s all about. In the Kenyan market brands like Bulleit, Tennessee is available, but do we ever recognise them as bourbon. Put simply, Bourbon is a type of American whiskey made primarily with corn. So, let’s get to the basics just in case you don’t know about Bourbon.